{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01CMfssqgTzux1gcAfUyWuJh","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I see the bugs. There are two issues in `handleAPIStepContent`:\n\n1. The `prompt` config value is `file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")` (with the `file(...)` wrapper), but the handler uses it as a raw file path\n2. The handler checks for `command` and `script` config keys, but the DSL uses `run` for script steps\n\nLet me also check what the frontend drawer displays for config keys.\n\nThe frontend `openDrawer` (line 263) also checks for `command` and `script` instead of `run`. Let me fix both the backend and frontend."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":449,"cache_read_input_tokens":45390,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":449},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a1047ed4-00a1-4630-bba4-fa269b61630e","uuid":"04330892-3944-4045-9f98-1afe1cab5fda"}
