{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01M9G91u9TdvRHBEJYXwxZYb","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Build succeeds. Here's a summary of the fix:\n\n**Root cause:** Two bugs in `handleAPIStepContent`:\n\n1. **`file(...)` wrapper not unwrapped** — The DSL parser stores prompt values as `file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")` (literal string with the `file()` wrapper). The handler tried to use this directly as a file path, so `os.ReadFile` failed.\n\n2. **Wrong config key names** — The handler checked for `command` and `script` config keys, but the DSL uses `run` for script steps.\n\n**Changes:**\n- `handler.go`: Added `extractFilePath()` helper to unwrap `file(\"...\")` references. Changed the handler to check for `run` config key and use `extractFilePath` on both `prompt` and `run` values.\n- `project_detail.html`: Updated the drawer to display the `run` config key (instead of `command`/`script`) and unwrap `file(...)` for cleaner display.\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":314,"cache_read_input_tokens":49941,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":314},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a1047ed4-00a1-4630-bba4-fa269b61630e","uuid":"2561cbc0-1357-45db-ab9e-563cf95386b3"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":125587,"duration_api_ms":90743,"num_turns":14,"result":"Build succeeds. Here's a summary of the fix:\n\n**Root cause:** Two bugs in `handleAPIStepContent`:\n\n1. **`file(...)` wrapper not unwrapped** — The DSL parser stores prompt values as `file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")` (literal string with the `file()` wrapper). The handler tried to use this directly as a file path, so `os.ReadFile` failed.\n\n2. **Wrong config key names** — The handler checked for `command` and `script` config keys, but the DSL uses `run` for script steps.\n\n**Changes:**\n- `handler.go`: Added `extractFilePath()` helper to unwrap `file(\"...\")` references. Changed the handler to check for `run` config key and use `extractFilePath` on both `prompt` and `run` values.\n- `project_detail.html`: Updated the drawer to display the `run` config key (instead of `command`/`script`) and unwrap `file(...)` for cleaner display.\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"a1047ed4-00a1-4630-bba4-fa269b61630e","total_cost_usd":0.577542,"usage":{"input_tokens":14,"cache_creation_input_tokens":37020,"cache_read_input_tokens":497044,"output_tokens":3903,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":37020,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":14,"outputTokens":3903,"cacheReadInputTokens":497044,"cacheCreationInputTokens":37020,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.577542,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"8cc66666-582a-45e5-8506-8a65713ee742"}
